WEBVTT

00:02:00.625 --> 00:02:02.184
I said to him,

00:02:02.208 --> 00:02:04.809
"Mijo, if your mom is here,

00:02:04.833 --> 00:02:07.583
I'm certain you will be reunited."

00:02:09.417 --> 00:02:11.500
When I walked out of the cell,

00:02:12.833 --> 00:02:15.768
an officer got close to me and said to me,

00:02:15.792 --> 00:02:17.375
"Sister, thank you.

00:02:18.292 --> 00:02:20.875
You have helped us realize

00:02:22.417 --> 00:02:23.875
that they are human beings."

00:02:25.792 --> 00:02:28.684
You know, sometimes,
no matter what job we have,

00:02:28.708 --> 00:02:32.184
we must never forget to recognize